{"word":"Mark, John","slug":"mark,-john","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Mark, John</b> - (Marcus) son of Mary, \"The Young Man who Recovered himself\"<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=12&verse=12'>Act 12:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=12&verse=25'>Act 12:25</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=13&verse=5'>Act 13:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=13&verse=13'>Act 13:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=15&verse=37'>Act 15:37</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=51&chapter=4&verse=10'>Col 4:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=55&chapter=4&verse=11'>2Ti 4:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=57&chapter=1&verse=24'>Phm 1:24</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=60&chapter=5&verse=13'>1Pe 5:13</a><p/>--Facts Concerning<p/>Had Godly Mother<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=12&verse=12'>Ac 12:12</a><p/>Related to Barnabas<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=51&chapter=4&verse=10'>Col 4:10</a><p/>Helper of Paul and Barnabas<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=12&verse=25'>Ac 12:25</a><p/>Early years apparently vacillating<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=13&verse=13'>Act 13:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=15&verse=38'>Act 15:38</a><p/>Later years became a faithful co-worker with Paul<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=51&chapter=4&verse=10'>Col 4:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=55&chapter=4&verse=11'>2Ti 4:11</a><p/>Companion of Peter<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=60&chapter=5&verse=13'>1Pe 5:13</a>"}]}